config

+ parent-provides
  + service ROM
  + service PD
  + service CPU
  + service LOG
  + service File_system

+ service File_system | + default-policy | + child chroot
+ service ROM         | + default-policy | + child fs_rom

+ start chroot | caps: 100 | ram: 3M
  + provides | + service File_system
  + route | + any-service | + parent
  + config
    + policy | label_prefix: rw -> | path: / | writeable: yes
    + policy | label_prefix: ro -> | path: / | writeable: no

+ start fs_rom | caps: 100 | ram: 10M
  + provides | + service ROM
  + config
  + route
    + service File_system | + child chroot | identity: ro
    + any-service         | + parent
-
